It feels like I've fallen into a strange loop with blogging: I can't write about what I don't know, and what I do know feels too simple to bother writing about 🤔. But that's just me making excuses. Ever since starting school in the fall, I haven't really sat down to think seriously; my brain seems to be in a kind of rigid state. Leaving this website empty feels lifeless, so I might as well try to loosen up my mindset. The words don't necessarily have to convey something to others; being able to express myself is enough.

So I'm going to continue indulging in games 🤡.
